The Prime Minister doesn't rule out a large-scale meeting, "not necessarily a summit", where they "create a shared vision".
The development of the region would otherwise be in line with the principles of sustainable development.
The Northern Plan will be coordinated, systematic and environmentally friendly", the Prime Minister promised.
