He also cooperated with the Zuschlages in the now-under-liquidation Biogate Kft., which in 2003 provided the Better Future Foundation, the Atlas Association and the Vörösfenyő Association with invoices worth roughly HUF 5 million, which were not backed by any real economic activity.
No cash flow, because the accounts were later cancelled, but the organizations forgot to include this in their documents.
